        "text": "This battering ram is fitted with a large metal drill powered by a clockwork engine. Once rammed into an object, the drill can be activated to weaken the structure against further strikes. Despite being a portable siege weapon, a drilling ram has the Load action, which represents winding the clockwork engine.",
